{"article_id":"3uMNqYy6ouhBTvQl","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A commander of Al Qaeda in Yemen is officially taking responsibility","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"for carefully planning , financing and carrying out the terror attacks on Charlie Hebdo in Paris last week .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"More from Fox News :","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"Al Qaeda 's affiliate in Yemen has released a video","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"claiming responsibility for last week 's deadly attack by two gunmen on the offices of the satirical newspaper Charlie Hebdo in Paris .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Nasr al-Ansi , a top commander of Al Qaeda in the Arabian Peninsula , or AQAP","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"as the branch is known ,","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"appeared in an 11-minute Internet video","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"posted Wednesday ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"that the massacre was in `` vengeance for the prophet . ''","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Al-Ansi also said in the video","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"that France belongs to the `` party of Satan ''","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and warned of more `` tragedies and terror . ''","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"He says","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Yemen 's Al Qaeda branch `` chose the target ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"laid out the plan","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"and financed the operation , ''","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"though he produced no evidence","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"to support the claim .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"It was revealed last week","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"that one of the brothers","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"who carried out the attack ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Saïd Kouachi ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"did his training in Yemen .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Just a few short months ago , President Obama touted anti-terrorism operations in Yemen and Somalia as a success","depth":4},{"id":26,"text":"and upheld them as examples of how the United States would fight ISIS .","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"POLL :","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"How should the White House respond to ISIS ?","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"Vote here .","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"The White House has also repeatedly argued","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"Al Qaeda is `` on the run ''","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"and that it 's core leaders have been `` decimated . ''","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"From his September 10 , 2014 speech at the White House :","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"Now , it will take time to eradicate a cancer like ISIL .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"And any time we take military action ,","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"there are risks involved","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"-- especially to the servicemen and women","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"who carry out these missions .","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"But I want the American people to understand how this effort will be different from the wars in Iraq and Afghanistan .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"It will not involve American combat troops","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"fighting on foreign soil .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"This counterterrorism campaign will be waged through a steady , relentless effort","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"to take out ISIL","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"wherever they exist ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"using our air power and our support for partner forces on the ground .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"This strategy","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"of taking out terrorists","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"who threaten us ,","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"while supporting partners on the front lines ,","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"is one","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"that we have successfully pursued in Yemen and Somalia for years .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"And it is consistent with the approach","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"I outlined earlier this year :","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"to use force against anyone","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"who threatens America ' s core interests ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"but to mobilize partners","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"wherever possible","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"to address broader challenges to international order .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"Chilling raw video shows the Kouachi brothers","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"yelling about vengeance for the prophet Mohammed","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"just after they murdered Charlie Hebdo editors","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"and left the scene .","depth":5},{"id":63,"text":"As Conn has reported ,","depth":4},{"id":64,"text":"the White House is still bending over backwards","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"to avoid using the term `` Islamic terror ''","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"to describe the attack .","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"How should the White House respond to ISIS ?","depth":3},{"id":68,"text":"Vote here .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":137,"left":127,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":93,"right":126,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":93,"left":70,"right":92,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":87,"right":91,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":72,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":2,"right":71,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":71,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":80,"right":85,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":77,"right":79,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":77,"left":75,"right":76,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":75,"left":73,"right":74,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":73,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"